A woman practices yoga with a goat standing on her back at a yoga school in Dallas, Texas, the United States, Nov. 17, 2019. The yoga school in Dallas invites people to play with goats when practicing yoga, attracting lots of people to participate in the new yoga exercise. (Photo by Tian Dan/Xinhua)   

